ced%2C%20even%20though%20she%20doesn't%20believe%20it's%20true.%20When%20she%20was%20in%20the%20office%2C%20she%20said%2C%20she%20witnessed%20plenty%20of%20people%20playing%20on%20their%20phones%20underneath%20their%20desks%20or%20scrolling%20Facebook.%20Just%20because%20someone's%20sitting%20in%20an%20office%20doesn't%20make%20them%20productive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20twist%3F%20Her%20old%20job%20has%20been%20posted%20online%20%E2%80%94%20listed%20as%20a%20remote%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompanies%20are%20going%20to%20realize%20if%20you%20want%20a%20diversity%20of%20talent%2C%20you%20cannot%20keep%20your%20circle%20small%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20open%20up%2C%20and%20if%20you're%20going%20to%20open%20up%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20open%20to%20hybrid%20or%20remote%20or%20a%20different%20way%20of%20being.%20I%20do%20think%20that%20companies%20are%20going%20to%20kind%20of%20be%20forced%20into%20this%20new%20way%20of%20working.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20strong%20feelings%20about%20remote%20work%20versus%20in-office%20work%3F%20Share%20your%20story%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajkaplan%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejkaplan%40insider.com.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanager-quit-over-rto-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692699301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e3b966b698ac0019de77ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanager-quit-over-rto-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Danielle%2C%20who%20works%20in%20digital%20marketing%2C%20thinks%20some%20managers%20who%20need%20their%20workers%20back%20in%20the%20office%20are%20just%20insecure%20and%20bad%20at%20their%20jobs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Juliana%