rrounding%20it.%20The%20home's%20garden%20also%20appears%20to%20have%20kept%20its%20greenery%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20ashes%20and%20charred%20trees.%20The%20miracle%20has%20left%20social%20media%20abuzz%2C%20with%20many%20users%20asking%20how%20it's%20possible.%20The%20house's%20owner%20has%20now%20opened%20up%20what%20she%20thinks%20helps%20it%20survive%20last%20week's%20fires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20100%25%20wood%20house%20so%20it's%20not%20like%20we%20fireproofed%20it%20or%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Dora%20Atwater%20Millikin%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fcalifornia%2Fstory%2F2023-08-18%2Fhow-did-the-red-house-survive-the-lahaina-fire%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELos%20Angeles%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Atwater%20Millikin%20and%20her%20husband%20Dudley%20recently%20renovated%20the%20100-year-old%20house%2C%20which%20they%20have%20owned%20for%20three%20years%2C%20without%20thinking%20about%20the%20wildfires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20love%20old%20buildings%2C%20so%20we%20just%20wanted%20to%20honor%20the%20building.%20And%20we%20didn't%20change%20the%20building%20in%20any%20way%20-%20we%20just%20restored%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Atwater%20Millikin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20one%20decision%20that%20helped%20the%20house%20escape%20a%20devastating%20fate%20was%20the%20couple's%20decision%20to%20replace%20the%20asphalt%20roof%20with%20one%20made%20out%20of%20heavy-gauge%20metal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20fire%2C%20there%20were%20pieces%20of%20wood%20-%206%2C%2012%20inches%20long%20-%20that%20were%20on%20fire%20and%20just%20almost%20floating%20through%20the%20air%20with%20the%20wind%20and%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Atwater%20Millikin%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3ELA%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20would%20hit%20people's%20roofs%2C%20and%20if%20it%20was%20an%20asphalt%20roof%2C%20it%20would%20catch%20on%20fire.%20And%20otherwise%2C%20they%20would%20fall%20off%20the%20roof%20and%20then%20ignite%20the%20foliage%20around%20the%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foliage%20around%20the%20house%20was%20also%20cut%20down%20and%20stones%20added%20to%20the%20ground%20surrounding%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20red-roofed%20house%20was%20not%20too%20close%20to%20neighbouring%20properties%2C%20instead%20shared%20border%20with%20the%20ocean%2C%20a%20road%20and%20an%20empty%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Ms%20Atwater%20Millikin%20and%20her%20husband%20plan%20to%20return%20to%20Maui%20soon%20and%20open%20their%20place%20to%20neighbours%20who%20were%20left%20homeless.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692695160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fio3eh97o_hawaii-wildfire-house-survives-afp-1200_625x300_22_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-did-viral-red-roofed-house-survive-hawaii-wildfires-owner-explains-4318687%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20images%20of%20the%20two-storey%20house%20in%20Hawaii%20were%20widely%20circulated%20on%20social%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-did-viral-red-roofed-house-survive-hawaii-wildfires-owner-explains-4318687%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-did-viral-red-roofed-house-survive-hawaii-wildfires-owner-explains-4318687%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-did-viral-red-roofed-house-survive-hawaii-wildfires-owner-explains-4318687%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20make%20up%20to%20%246%2C000%20a%20month%20selling%20Udemy%20courses%20for%20virtual%20assistants.%20Here's%20how%20I%20got%20started.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22headshot%20of%20Erin%20Booth%5C%22%20charset