se%20of%20the%20platform's%20access%20to%20millions%20of%20people.%20I%20knew%20that%20as%20a%20new%20course%20creator%20with%20virtually%20no%20audience%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20as%20wide%20of%20a%20reach%20on%20my%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20years%20later%2C%20I%20now%20have%2024%20courses%20listed%2C%20and%20they%20bring%20in%20between%20%243%2C000%20and%20%246%2C000%20a%20month.%20Here's%20how%20I%20got%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20asked%20myself%20what%20I%20wished%20I%20knew%20I%20when%20I%20started%20as%20a%20virtual%20assistant%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20there%20are%20many%20holes%20in%20the%20industry%20because%20there's%20no%20set%20path%20to%20becoming%20a%20virtual%20assistant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20course%20I%20released%20was%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dfd320e819721124065d92437dec5e9996e3dbdf3ae61572636e7cad9f82f5e8a%26postID%3D64e38ba0f87b369c6da4161f%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.udemy.com%252Fcourse%252Fgoogle-calendar-for-client-management%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecalendar%20management%20for%20executives%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20listed%20at%20%2469.99.%20I%20picked%20this%20topic%20because%20calendar%20management%20is%20a%20necessary%20skill%20for%20all%20virtual%20assistants%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20lot%20more%20nuanced%20than%20people%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20course%20content%20included%20tips%20and%20tricks%20I'd%20learned%20on%20my%20own%20through%20trial%20and%20error%20that%20I%20thought%20new%20or%20aspiring%20VAs%20could%20benefit%20from.%20From%20there%2C%20I%20continued%20to%20create%20courses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECourse%20creation%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20course%20takes%20about%20100%20hours%20to%20create%20from%20start%20to%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20process%20starts%20with%20brainstorming%20different%20topics%20that%20I%20think%20would%20be