20course%20to%20the%20platform.%20My%20courses%20vary%20in%20length%20%E2%80%94%20some%20courses%20are%20about%20three%20hours%2C%20while%20others%20are%20what%20I%20call%20%26quot%3Bmicro-courses%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20are%20about%2030%20minutes%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20keep%20my%20overhead%20as%20low%20as%20possible%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20few%20years%20of%20course%20creation%2C%20I%20used%20iMovie%20for%20editing%20and%20my%20phone%20for%20filming.%20The%20cost%20of%20making%20courses%20was%20basically%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20now%20have%20light%20boxes%2C%20a%20Yeti%20microphone%2C%20and%20editing%20software%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wondershare.net%2F%3Fgclid%3DCjwKCAiA_6yfBhBNEiwAkmXy51MuflT9qglI9b2WNXXroeTNTeBvEy3CorE5re3mnkpk6jDdGtY_tBoCmdsQAvD_BwE%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWonderShare%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20still%20film%20on%20my%20iPhone%2C%20but%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20iPhone%20camera%20is%20better%20than%20when%20I%20first%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPricing%20high%20doesn't%20work%20for%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tend%20to%20price%20my%20courses%20low%20compared%20to%20other%20courses%20on%20Udemy%2C%20which%20is%20something%20that%20other%20creators%20give%20me%20a%20hard%20time%20about.%20This%20pricing%20model%20works%20for%20me%20because%20it's%20a%20low%20barrier%20to%20entry%20that%20allows%20students%20to%20easily%20access%20the%20course%2C%20return%20to%20my%20other%20courses%20if%20they%20like%20it%2C%20and%20talk%20to%20me%20if%20they%20have%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%20offer%20two%20more%20expensive%20packages%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.erinbooth.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emy%20own%20site%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20courses%2C%20which%20I%20sell%20for%20%24199%20and%20%24599%2C%20include%20one-on-one%20personalized%20coaching.%20I%20price%20these%20courses%20higher%20be