%22Women%20Engaging%20in%20'Legal%20Terrorism'%20By%20'Misusing'%20Section%20on%20Cruelty%20By%20Husbands%3A%20Calcutta%20HC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F13112951%2FCalcutta_High_Court_-_Kolkata_2011-12-18_0328-copy.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20on%20Monday%20(August%2021)%20said%20that%20women%20are%20engaging%20in%20%E2%80%9Clegal%20terrorism%E2%80%9D%20by%20misusing%20Section%20498A%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%20The%20section%20criminalises%20cruelty%20against%20a%20woman%20by%20her%20husband%20or%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingle-judge%20Justice%20Subhendu%20Samanta%20said%20that%20though%20the%20section%20was%20brought%20it%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20welfare%2C%20it%20is%20now%20being%20%E2%80%9Cmisused%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20legislature%20has%20enacted%20the%20provision%20of%20Section%20498A%20to%20strike%20out%20the%20dowry%20menace%20from%20the%20society.%20But%20it%20is%20observed%20in%20several%20cases%20that%20by%20misusing%20of%20said%20provision%20new%20legal%20terrorism%20is%20unleashed%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fwomen-unleashed-legal-terrorism-misusing-section-498a-ipc-calcutta-high-court%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20the%20judge%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20criminal%20law%20allows%20a%20complainant%20to%20file%20a%20criminal%20complaint%20but%20the%20same%20has%20to%20be%20justified%20by%20adducing%20cogent%20evidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%20said%2C%20quashing%20charges%20under%20Section%20489A%20against%20a%20man%20and%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20specific%20case%2C%20the%20judge%20was%20hearing%20a%20plea%20filed%20by%20a%20man%20and%20his%20family%20members%20challenging%20the%20criminal%20cases%20lodged%20against%20them%20by%20his%20estranged%20wife%20in%20October%20and%20December%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20direct%20allegation%20against%20the%20husband%20by%20the%20de-facto%20complainant%20is%20merely%20from%20her%20version.%20It%20support%20no%20documentary%20or%20medical%20evidence.%20One%20neighbour%20has%20heard%20about%20the%20quarrel%20of%20the%20wife%20and%20her%20husband%3B%20the%20quarrel%20of%20two%20persons%20does%20not%20mean%20or%20prove%20who%20is%20in%20aggression%20or%20who%20is%20aggrieved%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20of%20a%20view%20that%20the%20instant%20criminal%20proceedings%20initiated%20by%20the%20de-facto%20complainant%20against%20the%20husband%20and%20in-laws%20does%20not%20disclose%20prima%20facie%20offence%20against%20them%20as%20alleged.%20The%20proceeding%20are%20instituted%20only%20to%20fulfil%20personal%20grudge.%20Considering%20the%20circumstances%20I%20think%20it%20necessary%20to%20invoke%20the%20inherent%20power%20of%20this%20court%20to%20quash%20the%20proceedings%20otherwise%20the%20continuation%20of%20the%20criminal%20proceedings%20would%20be%20tantamount%20to%20the%20abuse%20of%20process%20of%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692694810000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F13112951%2FCalcutta_High_Court_-_Kolkata_2011-12-18_0328-copy.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwomen-engaging-in-legal-terrorism-by-misusing-section-on-cruelty-by-husbands-calcutta-hc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Single-judge%20Justice%20Subhendu%20Samanta%20said%20that%20though%20the%20section%20was%20brought%20it%20for%20women's%20welfare%2C%20it%20is%20now%20being%20%26quot%3Bmisused%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20first%20large%20cruise%20ship%20built%20in%20China%20complete%20with%20a%20water%20