%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F07085318%2FChina-india.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMilitary%20officials%20from%20India%20and%20China%20on%20Monday%2C%20August%2021%2C%20held%20talks%20to%20resolve%20the%20border%20standoff%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20sensitive%20Depsang%20plains.%20It%20was%20the%20third%20such%20meeting%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20four%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intense%20round%20of%20discussions%20between%20Major%20General-level%20officials%20from%20both%20sides%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20a%20few%20days%20assumes%20significance%20given%20the%20expectation%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20would%20meet%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20three-day%20BRICS%20summit%2C%20which%20began%20in%20Johannesburg%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20August%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilitary%20officials%20from%20both%20sides%20have%20been%20entrusted%20with%20the%20responsibility%20to%20find%20a%20workable%20solution%20that%20could%20be%20implemented%20along%20the%20undemarcated%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fnation%2Fdepsang-on-table-india-china-hold-third-meet-in-4-days-537029%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20April%202020%2C%20both%20sides%20have%20been%20caught%20in%20a%20border%20standoff%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh.%20There%20are%20particular%20differences%20over%20pulling%20troops%20back%20from%20the%20Depsang%20plains%20and%20Charding%20Nullah%20near%20Demchok.%20The%20dispute%20is%20concerning%20a%20972%20sq%20km%20plateau%20Depsang.%20Both%20have%20issues%20regarding%20troop%20positions%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbottleneck%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20eastern%20edge%20of%20Depsang.%20India%20has%20been%20opposed%20to%20the%20Chinese%20Army%20deliberating%20preventing%20the%20movement%20of%20Indian%20patrols%20on%20the%20patrolling%20route%20that%20goes%20east%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbottleneck%E2%80%9D%20in%20Depsang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20April%202020%2C%20when%20the%20standoff%20began%2C%20Indian%20patrols%20had%20been%20using%20the%20patrolling%20route.%20However%2C%20since%20then%2C%20China%20has%20been%20referring%20to%20a%20controversial%2030-year-old%20border%20agreement%20to%20prevent%20the%20movement%20of%20Indian%20patrols.%20According%20to%20the%20said%20agreement%2C%20patrolling%20parties%20of%20one%20side%20should%20return%20upon%20encountering%20the%20patrol%20party%20of%20the%20other%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20crucial%20things%20that%20came%20up%20during%20the%20discussion%20was%20that%20the%20Indian%20troops%20would%20coordinate%20with%20the%20Chinese%20when%20patrols%20go%20east%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbottleneck%E2%80%9D.%20This%20means%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20new%20buffer%20zone%2C%20and%20patrols%20cannot%20be%20held%20independently%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20have%20competing%20claims%20in%20the%20region%2C%20particularly%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20Depsang%20plains.%20Some%20of%20these%20contested%20points%20have%20great%20strategic%20value%2C%20for%20they%20overlook%20the%20Aksai%20Chin%20plateau%20which%20is%20under%20the%20illegal%20control%20of%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20sources%2C%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2Fdefence-india-china-eastern-ladakh-disengagement-talks-promoting-confidence-and-cooperation-for-border-stability-3215648%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Major%20General%20Prasanna%20Mishra%20represented%20the%20Indian%20delegation%20for%20%E2%80%9Cengaging%20in%20productive%20deliberations%20with%20his%20Chinese%20counterpart%E2%80%9D.%20Major%20General%20Mishra%20commands%20the%20Indian%20Army%E2%80%99s%203%20Division%2C%20which%20is%20tasked%20with%20securing%20and%20managing%20the%20832-kilometer-long%20LAC%20specifically%20within%20the%20Ladakh%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20proposing%20to%20China%20that%20a%20phased%20three-step%20process%20is%20necessary%20to%20resolve%20the%20standoff.%20The%20first%20of%20these%20includes%20the%20disengagement%20of%20troops%20within%20close%20proximity%20in%20grey%20zones%20along%20the%20LAC%20and%20moving%20back%20to%20positions%20as%20on%20April%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20next%20two%20steps%2C%20India%20suggests%20that%20there%20should%20be%20de-escalation%20and%20de-induction%2C%20which%20includes%20pulling%20troops%20and%20equipment%20back%20to%20the%20scenario%20before%20April%202020.%20Until%20that%20happens%2C%20India%20says%20the%20situation%20cannot%20be%20viewed%20as%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692693023000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F07085318%2FChina-india.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Famid-buzz-of-modi-xi-meeting-india-china-hold-three-military-level-talks-on-lac-in-four-days%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Major-General%20officials%20from%20both%20sides%20met%20to%20resolve%20the%20border%20standoff%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20sensitive%20Depsang%20plains.%C2%A0Meanwhile%2C%20news%20is%20making%20rounds%20that%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Xi%20Jinping%20would%20meet%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20ongoing%20BRICS%20summit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Famid-buzz-of-modi-xi-meeting-india-china-hold-three-military-level-talks-on-lac-in-four-days%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Singer%20Raju%20Punjabi%20passes%20away%20due%20to%20jaundice%3B%20know%20its%20signs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692693000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102938439%2Cimgsize-1045750.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Fhealth-fitness%2Fhealth-news%2Fsinger-raju-punjabi-passes-away-due-to-jaundice-know-what-it-is-and-what-are-its-signs%2Farticleshow%2F102938412.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Haryana%20singer%20Raju%20Punjabi%20passed%20away%20on%20Tuesday%20due%20to%20jaundice.%20The%2040%20year%20old%20was%20getting%20treated%20for%20the%20same.%20Jaundice%20is%20a%20medical%20condition%20characterized%20by%20the%20yellowing%20of%20the%20skin%2C%20mucous%20membranes%2C%20and%20the%20whites%20of%20the%20eyes.%20It%20occurs%20due%20to%20an%20excess%20buildup%20of%20a%20yellow%20pigment%20called%20bilirubin%20in%20the%20blood%20and%20tissues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Fhealth-fitness%2Fhealth-news%2Fsinger-raju-punjabi-passes-away-due-to-jaundice-know-what-it-is-and-what-are-its-signs%2Farticleshow%2F102938412.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20Just%20Teesta%20Setalvad...%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court's%20New%20SOP%20Helps%20Rape%20Survivor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-pass-order-against-superior-court-supreme-court-raps-gujarat-high-court-4314860%5C%22%3Eswift%20response%20to%20a%20rape%20survivor's%20plea%20seeking%20permission%20for%20abortion%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20the%20result%20of%20new%20guidelines%20prepared%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20for%20urgent%20cases%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20new%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedure%20(SOP)%2C%20%26quot%3Bexceptionally%20urgent%26quot%3B%20matters%20may%20be%20flagged%20to%20the%20court's%20mentioning%20officer%20by%2010.30%20am.%20The%20officer%20will%20then%20place%20it%20before%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20whenever%20%26quot%3Bduring%20lunch%20recess%20or%20as%20the%20exigency%20may%20warrant%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20guidelines%20say.%20The%20SOP%20also%20has%20the%20provision%20of%20sending%20across%20such%20requests%20over%20email%3B%20these%20emails%20are%20closely%20tracked%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%2C%20said%20sources%20from%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court's%20late-night%20bail%20relief%20to%20activist%20Teesta%20Setalvad%20and%20an%20urgent%20hearing%20on%20the%20recent%20communal%20clashes%20in%20Nuh%20are%20among%20key%20cases%20that%20were%20taken%20up%20as%20per%20this%20SOP%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Teesta%20Setalvad%20case%2C%20being%20heard%20on%20a%20Saturday%20night%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fteesta-setalvad-a-bharatnatyam-backstory-to-activist-teesta-setalvads-late-night-reprieve-4170310%5C%22%3EChief%20Justice%20had%20stepped%20out%20of%20a%20Bharatnatyam%3C%2Fa%3E%20event%20to%20hold%20discussions%20with%20brother%20judges.%20In%20the%20Nuh%20case%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffor-haryana-violence-petition-a-rare-move-by-supreme-court-chief-justice-4262465%5C%22%3Ea%20Constitution%20bench%20hearing%20a%20plea%20on%20Article%20370%20was%20paused%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20that%20a%20judge%20could%20complete%20the%20urgent%20hearing%20in%20the%20Haryana%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20criticised%20for%20the%20late-night%20reprieve%20to%20activist%20Teesta%20Setalvad%2C%20with%20many%20saying%20the%20swift%20response%20was%20because%20she%20was%20a%20known%20name.%20What%20about%20this%20case%2C%20then%3F%20The%20court%20is%20just%20following%20the%20new%20SOP%20for%20urgent%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20highly-placed%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20yesterday%20allowed%20the%20rape%20survivor%20to%20terminate%20the%20nearly%2028-week%20pregnancy%20following%20a%20medical%20board's%20report%20that%20she%20is%20fit%20for%20the%20procedure.%20The%20court%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20Gujarat%20High%20Court%20for%20passing%20an%20order%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20listed%20the%20matter%20for%20hearing.%20The%20high%20court%20had%20rejected%20the%20plea%20for%20abortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20happening%20in%20Gujarat%20High%20Court%3F%20No%20court%20in%20India%20can%20pass%20an%20order%20against%20a%20superior%20court%20order.%20It%20is%20against%20constitutional%20philosophy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20B%20V%20Nagarathna%20and%20Justice%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20said%20after%20it%20learnt%20of%20the%20high%20court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20representing%20the%20Gujarat%20government%2C%20had%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20high%20court%20passed%20the%20order%20to%20fix%20a%20%26quot%3Bclerical%20error%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20clerical%20error%20in%20the%20previous%20order%20and%20that%20was%20fixed%20on%20Saturday.%20It%20was%20a%20misunderstanding%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20earlier%20flagged%20the%20delay%20by%20the%20high%20court%20in%20deciding%20the%20rape%20survivor's%20petition%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bvaluable%20time%26quot%3B%20had%20been%20lost.%20%26quot%3BIn%20such%20cases%2C%20there%20must%20be%2C%20not%20undue%20urgency%2C%20but%20at%20least%20a%20sense%20of%20urgency%20in%20such%20matters%20and%20not%20a%20lackadaisical%20attitude%20of%20treating%20it%20as%20any%20normal%20case%20and%20just%20adjourning%20it.%20We%20are%20sorry%20to%20say%20and%20make%20this%20remark%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692692820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fbfidjl98_dy-chandrachud_625x300_16_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-chie