ndian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%2C%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20is%20set%20to%20land%20on%20the%20moon%20on%20August%2023%2C%20around%2018%3A04%20hours%20IST.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELive%20action%20will%20be%20available%20on%20the%20ISRO%20website%2C%20its%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20Facebook%2C%20and%20public%20broadcaster%20DD%20National%20TV%20from%2017%3A27%20IST%20on%20Aug%2023%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20be%20the%20fourth%20country%20in%20the%20world%20to%20achieve%20this%20feat%20after%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20China%2C%20but%20India%20will%20be%20the%20only%20country%20in%20the%20world%20to%20land%20on%20the%20lunar%20south%20pole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20objectives%20of%C2%A0Chandrayaan-3%C2%A0mission%20are%20threefold%20--%20to%20demonstrate%20safe%20and%20soft%20landing%20on%20lunar%20surface%3B%20to%20demonstrate%C2%A0rover%C2%A0roving%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20and%20to%20conduct%20in-situ%20scientific%20experiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3's%20development%20phase%20commenced%20in%20January%202020%20with%20the%20launch%20planned%20sometime%20in%202021.%20However%2C%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20brought%20an%20unforeseen%20delay%20to%20the%20mission's%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%C2%A0mission%20was%20launched%20on%20July%2014%2C%202023%20via%20the%20GSLV%20Mark%203%20(LVM%203)%20heavy-lift%20launch%20vehicle%20from%20the%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Centre%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Sriharikota%20at%202%3A35%20PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692692760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2Fim842bf8_prakash-raj_625x300_21_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcase-filed-against-actor-prakash-raj-for-mocking-chandrayaan-3-43