3A30%20am%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20bench%20started%20the%20hearing.%20It%20raised%20questions%20on%20the%20delay%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20High%20Court%2C%20and%20constituted%20a%20new%20medical%20board%20with%20instructions%20to%20file%20the%20report%20in%2024%20hours%2C%20by%20Sunday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20after%20seeing%20the%20report%20of%20the%20Medical%20Board%2C%20allowed%20the%2028-week-pregnant%20woman%20to%20have%20an%20abortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSubsequent%20to%20the%20medical%20procedure%20to%20be%20carried%20out%2C%20in%20the%20event%20the%20foetus%20is%20found%20to%20be%20alive%2C%20the%20hospital%20is%20to%20give%20all%20facilities%20including%20incubation%20to%20ensure%20the%20foetus%20survives.%20The%20State%20shall%20then%20take%20steps%20to%20ensure%20the%20child%20is%20adopted%20in%20accordance%20with%20law%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-pass-order-against-superior-court-supreme-court-raps-gujarat-high-court-4314860%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20the%20judgment%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20on%20humanitarian%20grounds%2C%20suggested%20that%20if%20the%20foetus%20is%20alive%20during%20the%20abortion%20process%2C%20the%20government%20can%20take%20care%20of%20it%2C%20and%20then%20take%20steps%20for%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mehta%20mentioned%20an%20earlier%20incident%20where%20a%20minor%2C%20who%20was%20initially%20insisting%20on%20termination%20of%20her%20pregnancy%2C%20was%20persuaded%20to%20give%20birth%20to%20the%20child%2C%20and%20it%20was%20given%20for%20adoption%20after%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%20in%20the%20top%20court%2C%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20has%20also%20included%20the%20facility%20to%20e-mail%20in%20the%20Standard%20operating%20Procedure%20prepared%20for%20hearing%20urgent%20cases.%20The%20CJI%20personally%20monitors%20this%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Registrar%20has%20been%20instructed%20to%20inform%20the%20CJI%20about%20urgent%20matters%20so%20that%20a%20bench%20can%20be%20formed%2C%20and%20the%20matter%20heard%20on%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20disappointed%20that%20the%20high%20court%20passed%20an%20order%20on%20Saturday%2C%20even%20after%20it%20had%20listed%20the%20matter%20for%20Sunday.%20The%20high%20court%20had%20refused%20relief%20to%20the%20petitioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20happening%20in%20Gujarat%20High%20Court%3F%20No%20court%20in%20India%20can%20pass%20an%20order%20against%20a%20superior%20court%20order.%20It%20is%20against%20constitutional%20philosophy%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20accepted%20the%20request%20of%20SG%20Tushar%20Mehta%20not%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Nagarathna%2C%20though%2C%20while%20making%20oral%20observations%2C%20said%20that%20crucial%20time%20was%20lost%20due%20to%20the%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2025-year-old%20survivor%20claims%20that%20the%20pregnancy%20was%20detected%20on%20August%204.%20Her%20counsel%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20she%20approached%20the%20court%20on%20August%207%20and%20the%20matter%20was%20heard%20the%20next%20day.%20The%20high%20court%20on%20August%208%20directed%20that%20a%20medical%20board%20be%20formed%20to%20look%20into%20the%20status%20of%20the%20petitioner's%20pregnancy%20and%20her%20health%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20medical%20college%20examined%20the%20rape%20survivor%20and%20submitted%20its%20report%20on%20August%2010.%20The%20report%2C%20the%20petitioner's%20counsel%20said%2C%20had%20ruled%20that%20the%20pregnancy%20can%20be%20terminated%2C%20but%20the%20High%20Court%20adjourned%20the%20matter%20for%20August%2017%2C%20and%20then%20did%20not%20even%20issue%20an%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20then%20came%20to%20know%20that%20her%20request%20was%20rejected%2C%20and%20knocked%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20doors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20noted%20that%20the%20report%20was%20taken%20on%20record%20by%20the%20high%20court%20on%20August%2011%20but%20%26quot%3Bstrangely%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20matter%20was%20listed%2012%20days%20later%2C%20%26quot%3Blosing%20sight%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20every%20day's%20delay%20was%20crucial%20and%20of%20great%20significance%20having%20regard%20to%20the%20facts%20and%20circumstances%20of%20the%20case%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20such%20cases%2C%20there%20must%20be%2C%20not%20undue%20urgency%2C%20but%20at%20least%20a%20sense%20of%20urgency%20in%20such%20matters%20and%20not%20a%20lackadaisical%20attitude%20of%20treating%20it%20as%20any%20normal%20case%20and%20just%20adjourning%20it.%20We%20are%20sorry%20to%20say%20and%20make%20this%20remark%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%20in%20oral%20observations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692692160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-allows-rape-survivor-to-abort-12-days-vs-12-hour-how-chief-justice-fast-tracked-rape-survivors-abortion-request-4318485%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Gujarat%20High%20Court%20wasted%2012%20crucial%20days%20in%20allowing%20a%20rape%20survivor%20to%20have%20an%20abortion%20in%20the%2026th%20week%20of%20her%20pregnancy%2C%20while%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20allowed%20the%20victim%20to%20have%20an%20abortion%20within%2012%20hours.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-allows-rape-survivor-to-abort-12-days-vs-12-hour-how-chief-justice-fast-tracked-rape-survivors-abortion-request-4318485%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-allows-rape-survivor-to-abort-12-days-vs-12-hour-how-chief-justice-fast-tracked-rape-survivors-abortion-request-4318485%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-allows-rape-survivor-to-abort-12-days-vs-12-hour-how-chief-justice-fast-tracked-rape-survivors-abortion-request-4318485%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2226%2F11%20Accused%20Tahawwur%20Rana's%20Extradition%20To%20India%20Stayed%20By%20US%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOverriding%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20appeal%2C%20a%20US%20court%20has%20ordered%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20extradition%20of%20Pakistani-origin%20Canadian%20businessman%20Tahawwur%20Rana%2C%20to%20India%20where%20he%20is%20facing%20a%20trial%20for%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%20has%20appealed%20before%20the%20Ninth%20Circuit%20Court%20against%20the%20order%20by%20a%20US%20District%20Court%20in%20the%20Central%20District%20of%20California%20that%20denied%20the%20writ%20of%20habeas%20corpus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Judge%20Dale%20S.%20Fischer%20of%20the%20US%20District%20Court%20in%20Central%20California%20in%20his%20latest%20order%20said%20that%20Rana's%20%E2%80%9Cex%20parte%20application%E2%80%9D%20seeking%20a%20stay%20on%20his%20extradition%20is%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20extradition%20of%20Rana%20to%20India%20is%20stayed%20pending%20the%20conclusion%20of%20his%20appeal%20before%20the%20United%20States%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20for%20the%20Ninth%20Circuit%2C%E2%80%9D%20Judge%20Fischer%20said%20in%20the%20order%20issued%20on%20August%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20doing%20so%20the%20judge%20overrode%20the%20government's%20recommendations%20that%20there%20should%20be%20no%20stay%20on%20Rana's%20extradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%20faces%20charges%20for%20his%20role%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20attacks%20and%20is%20known%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20Pakistani-American%20terrorist%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20conspirators%20of%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Court%20does%20not%20find%20that%20Rana%20%E2%80%9Chas%20made%20a%20strong%20showing%20that%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20succeed%20on%20the%20merits%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20otherwise%20the%20Court%20would%20have%20ruled%20in%20his%20favour%20in%20the%20first%20instance%20%E2%80%93%20he%20has%20certainly%20raised%20serious%20legal%20questions%20going%20to%20the%20merits%2C%20the%20judge%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20proper%20meaning%20of%20%E2%80%9Coffence%E2%80%9D%20in%20Article%206(1)%20of%20the%20extradition%20treaty%20is%20not%20clear%20and%20different%20jurists%20could%20come%20to%20different%20conclusions.%20Rana's%20position%20is%20certainly%20colourable%20and%20could%20very%20well%20be%20found%20to%20be%20correct%20on%20appeal%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20final%20two%20factors%20%E2%80%9Cmerge%20when%20the%20Government%20is%20the%20opposing%20party.%E2%80%9D%20There%20is%20value%20in%20compliance%20with%20India's%20extradition%20request%2C%20but%20Rana's%20extradition%20proceedings%20have%20been%20going%20on%20for%20more%20than%20three%20years%2C%20which%20suggests%20that%20the%20process%20has%20not%20been%20rushed%20so%20far.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20public%20interest%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20favours%20Rana%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20public%20has%20a%20strong%20interest%20in%20the%20proper%20interpretation%20of%20extradition%20treaties%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20interpretation%20of%20provisions%20that%20provide%20important%20individual%20protections%20like%20the%20one%20at%20issue%20here.%20Further%2C%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20public%20interest%20in%20definitive%2C%20binding%20interpretations%20of%20treaties.%20District%20courts%20cannot%20provide%20those%20rulings%3B%20courts%20of%20appeals%20can%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%20wrote%2C%20throwing%20the%20legal%20battle%20to%20the%20Ninth%20Circuit%20Court%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20for%20the%20Ninth%20Circuit%20has%20asked%20Rana%20to%20submit%20his%20argument%20before%20October%2010%20and%20the%20US%20Government%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20submit%20its%20response%20by%20November%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Fischer%20wrote%20that%20Rana%20has%20shown%20that%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20suffer%20significant%20irreparable%20harm%20absent%20a%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20be%20extradited%20to%20India%20for%20a%20trial%20on%20serious%20crimes%20with%20no%20hope%20for%20a%20review%20of%20his%20arguments%20or%20hope%20for%20his%20return%20to%20the%20United%20States.%20The%20government%20admits%20this%2C%20but%20then%20argues%20that%20because%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20claimed%20irreparable%20harm%20applies%20categorically%20to%20any%20fugitive%20who%20seeks%20a%20stay%20of%20extradition%20pending%20appeal%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20does%20not%20count%2C%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20the%20US%20attorney%20John%20J%20Lulejian%20appealed%20before%20the%20District%20Court%20to%20deny%20Rana's%20exparte%20application%20for%20a%20stay%20of%20extradition%20pending%20appeal%20and%20argued%20that%20the%20stay%20would%20cause%20%E2%80%9Cunwarranted%20delay%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20United%20States'%20fulfilment%20of%20its%20obligations%20to%20India%20and%20this%20will%20damage%20its%20credibility%20in%20the%20international%20arena%20and%20impair%20its%20ability%20to%20obtain%20the%20cooperation%20of%20foreign%20nations%20in%20bringing%20United%20States%20fugitives%20to%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%2C%20he%20argued%2C%20cannot%20show%20a%20likelihood%20of%20success%20on%20the%20merits%20of%20his%20claims%20or%20otherwise%20meet%20his%20burden%20of%20justifying%20a%20stay.%20%E2%80%9CAccordingly%2C%20the%20United%20States%20respectfully%20requests%20that%20the%20Court%20deny%20his%20ex%20parte%20application%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20US%20attorney%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELulejian%20argued%20that%20the%20District%20Court%20should%20deny%20Rana's%20request%20for%20a%20stay%20for%20the%20threshold%20reason%20that%20he%20has%20failed%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20obtain%20a%20reversal%20of%20this%20Court's%20decision%20in%20the%20Ninth%20Circuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20ex%20parte%20application%20for%20a%20stay%2C%20Rana%20has%20made%20no%20showing%20whatsoever%2C%20let%20alone%20a%20strong%20showing%2C%20that%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20succeed%20on%20the%20merits%20of%20his%20appeal%2C%20he%20argued.%20Indeed%2C%20he%20simply%20states%20that%20he%20seeks%20a%20stay%20%E2%80%9Cto%20permit%20his%20non-bis%20in%20idem%20argument%20to%20be%20heard%20by%20the%20court%20of%20appeals.%E2%80%9D%20India's%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20is%20probing%20Rana's%20role%20in%20the%2026%2F11%20attacks%20carried%20out%20by%20terrorists%20of%20the%20Pakistan-based%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20group.%20The%20NIA%20has%20said%20that%20it%20is%20ready%20to%20initiate%20proceedings%20to%20bring%20him%20to%20India%20through%20diplomatic%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%20166%20people%2C%20including%20six%20Americans%2C%20were%20killed%20in%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20in%20which%2010%20Pakistani%20terrorists%20laid%20a%20more%20than%2060-hour%20siege%2C%20attacking%20and%20killing%20people%20at%20iconic%20and%20vital%20locations%20of%20Mumbai.%20PTI%20LKJ%20AMS%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692692040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-01%2Fijes6u1_mumbai-attack-plotter-tahawwur-rana_625x300_14_January_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-court-stays-extradition-on-26-11-a