0a%20fact%20-%20that%20hockey%20is%20no%20longer%20producing%20any%20star%20players%20world%20over.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22JASPREET%20SAHNI%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A162%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fhockey%2Ftop-stories%2Findia-have-a-really-good-chance-of-winning-asian-games-gold-hockey-is-no-longer-producing-stars-former-pakistan-hockey-star-rehan-butt%2Farticleshow%2F102935027.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NMC%20Guidelines%3A%20Doctors'%20Orgs%20Find%20'Novel'%20Ways%20to%20Organise%20Conferences%20Without%20Pharma%20Backing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22123040%2Fsasun-bughdaryan-RlIppR1I3E8-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20new%20guidelines%20of%20the%20National%20Medical%20Commission%20(NMC)%20came%20into%20force%20through%20a%20gazetted%20notification%20dated%20August%202%2C%202023%2C%20various%20medical%20associations%20across%20India%20are%20trying%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20organise%20their%20conferences%20to%20overcome%20the%20limitations%20imposed%20by%20the%20new%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmc.org.in%2FMCIRest%2Fopen%2FgetDocument%3Fpath%3D%2FDocuments%2FPublic%2FPortal%2FLatestNews%2FNMC%2520RMP%2520Conduct%2520Regulations%25202023.pdf%5C%22%3ENMC%20guidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%20prohibit%20doctors%20from%20attending%20medical%20conferences%2C%20also%20known%20as%20CPDs%20(Continuing%20Professional%20Development%20programmes)%2C%20which%20are%20sponsored%20by%20pharmaceutical%20companies.%20However%2C%20this%20prohibition%20was%20meant%20for%20individual%20doctors%20only%2C%20and%20not%20their%20associations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NMC%20guidelines%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CRegistered%20medical%20practitioners%20(RMPs)%20should%20not%20be%20involved%20in%20any%20third-party%20educational%20activity%20like%20CPD%2C%20seminar%2C%20workshop%2C%20symposia%2C%20conference%2C%20etc.%2C%20which%20involves%20direct%20or%20indirect%20sponsorships%20from%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20or%20the%20allied%20health%20sector.%20RMP%20should%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20conflict-of-interest%20situations%20that%20may%20arise.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Association%20of%20Physicians%20of%20India%20(API)%20held%20a%20meeting%20at%205%20pm%20on%20August%2021.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20possesses%20a%20copy%20of%20%E2%80%98conclusive%20pointers%E2%80%99%20which%20were%20circulated%20after%20the%20meeting.%20The%20API%2C%20which%20according%20to%20the%20website%20is%20an%20association%20of%2020%2C000%20doctors%2C%20suggested%20its%20members%20take%20a%20different%20route%20for%20organising%20such%20conferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9C%5BThe%5D%20Societies%2FAssociations%20can%20officially%20receive%20money%20from%20Pharmas%20to%20organise%20a%20conference%2FCPD%2C%20but%20pharma%20cannot%20sponsor%20an%20individual%20doctor%20(any%20kind%20of%20individual%20sponsorship%20such%20as%20registration%2C%20travel%2C%20stay%20for%20a%20conference%20is%20not%20allowed).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20delegation%20of%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%20also%20met%20Union%20health%20minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20on%20August%2021%20evening%20with%20a%20request%20that%20this%20norm%20be%20done%20away%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20IMA%20president%20Dr%20Sharad%20Kumar%20Agarwal%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20the%20doctors%20keep%20themselves%20informed%20with%20new%20knowledge%20if%20such%20conferences%20are%20not%20organised%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20that%20purpose%20we%20need%20money.%20Otherwise%20from%20where%20would%20the%20money%20come%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20that%20there%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fnews%2Fhealth%2Fthere-s-an-unhealthy-alliance-between-doctors-and-pharma-firms-64230%5C%22%3Edocumented%20instances%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20conflict%20of%20interest%20and%20corruption%20linked%20with%20pharma-backed%20conferences%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20prejudice%20and%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20in%20it%E2%80%A6Such%20words%20should%20be%20avoided.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Agarwal%20said%20the%20IMA%20believes%20that%20all%20future%20medical%20conferences%20should%20be%20organised%20by%20various%20doctors%E2%80%99%20associations%20%E2%80%93%20something%20that%20the%20API%20also%20mentioned%20in%20the%20pointers%2C%20as%20mentioned%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Punjab%20Medical%20Council%20president%20and%20someone%20who%20has%20for%20a%20long%20time%20tried%20to%20highlight%20the%20illicit%20practices%20of%20his%20profession%2C%20Dr%20G.S.%20Grewal%2C%20said%20that%20it%20was%20wrong%20to%20say%20that%20if%20pharma%20companies%20stopped%20sponsorships%2C%20the%20conferences%20would%20cease%20to%20happen.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20pay%20for%20them%E2%80%A6each%20and%20every%20delegate%20is%20supposed%20to%20pay%20what%20is%20known%20as%20registration%20fee.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Grewal%20said%20it%20was%20possible%20that%20such%20medical%20conferences%20be%20organised%20without%20logistical%20and%20monetary%20support%20of%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20but%20sans%20what%20he%20called%20%E2%80%9Clavish%20lunches%20in%20big%2C%20five-star%20hotels%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20know%20of%20many%20instances%20where%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20went%20on%20to%20book%20air%20tickets%20and%20reserve%20hotel%20rooms%20%E2%80%93%20let%20alone%20paying%20the%20registration%20fee%2C%E2%80%9D%20Grewal%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NMC%20guidelines%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%5BAn%5D%20RMP%20himself%20or%20as%20part%20of%20any%20society%2C%20organisation%2C%20association%2C%20trust%2C%20etc.%20make%20regarding%20the%20relationship%20with%20the%20pharmaceutical%20and%20allied%20health%20sector%20industry%20clear%20and%20transparent%20open%20to%20scrutiny.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20API%20told%20its%20members%20on%20August%2021%20that%20no%20tax%20rebates%20should%20be%20sought%20to%20avoid%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%5BThe%5D%20best%20way%20for%20a%20Society%2FAssociation%20to%20avoid%20any%20scrutiny%20is%20to%20pay%20the%20full%20tax%20(as%20applicable)%20after%20its%20conference%2FCPD%20%5BContinuing%20Professional%20Development%20programme%5D%20is%20done%20with%3B%20do%20not%20try%20to%20save%20on%20tax%20returns%20even%20though%20the%20association%20is%20registered%20with%20the%20charity%20Commissioner%2C%C2%A0%20as%20the%20Income%20Tax%20office%20clearly%20looks%20upon%20the%20conference%2FCPD%20as%20a%20commercial%20activity%20done%20in%20a%20commercial%20premises%20(such%20as%20a%20five%20star%20hotel).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20current%20form%20of%20the%20NMC%20regulations%2C%20if%20a%20registered%20doctor%20is%20found%20violating%20this%20norm%2C%20s%2Fhe%20is%20liable%20to%20punished%20as%20per%20level%203%20of%20the%20punishments%20of%20the%20NMC%20guidelines%2C%20which%20stipulate%20suspension%20of%20licence%20to%20practise%20for%20a%20period%20of%20maximum%20of%20three%20months%20after%20a%C2%A0%20registration%20of%20complaints%20and%20inquiry%20at%20multiple%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fgovernment%2Fgovernment-supreme-court-pharma-doctor%2Famp%5C%22%3EUnion%20Govt%20Flips%20Stance%2C%20Tells%20SC%20%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20Push%20for%20Mandatory%20Rules%20to%20Curb%20Pharma-Doctor%20Nexus%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20health%20minister%2C%20according%20to%20the%20IMA%20president%2C%20had%20told%20the%20delegation%20that%20he%20would%20look%20into%20the%20demand%2C%20but%20did%20not%20specifically%20say%20anything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20medical%20conferences%2C%20whose%20dates%20for%20organisation%20had%20been%20declared%2C%20now%20stand%20cancelled%20or%20postponed%20due%20to%20the%20NMC%20gazetted%20notification.%20Dr%20Anirduddha%20Malpani%2C%20a%20renowned%20IVF%20specialist%20based%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmalpani%2Fstatus%2F1693617632292036913%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Eshared%3C%2Fa%3E%20two%20such%20instances%20on%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20chapter%20of%20the%20Cardiological%20Society%20of%20India%20has%20postponed%20the%20CARDICON-2023%2C%20slated%20to%20be%20held%20in%20September%20at%20Patna%E2%80%99s%20Hotel%20Maurya.%20In%20a%20note%20to%20its%20members%20it%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6the%20executive%20committee%20has%20decided%20that%20due%20to%20the%20unprecedented%20development%20%5Bthat%20has%5D%20taken%20place%20because%20of%20above%20notification%20%5BNMC%20gazetted%20notification%20issued%20on%20August%202%5D%20Cardicon-2023%20is%20going%20to%20be%20postponed%20till%20actual%20clarification%20%5Bis%5D%20received%20from%20National%20Medical%20Commission%20or%20Cardiological%20Society%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20GSICON-2023%2C%20which%20was%20slated%20to%20be%20held%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20August%20for%20specialists%20in%20geriatric%20medicine%2C%20has%20been%20cancelled%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdifficulties%20to%20organise%20it%20in%20view%20of%20recent%20guidelines%20issued%20by%20the%20NMC%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20its%20organisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGeneric%20drugs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20issue%20against%20which%20the%20doctors%20are%20up%20in%20arms%20pertains%20to%20the%20prescription%20guidelines%20made%20by%20the%20NMC.%20The%20guidelines%20state%20that%20doctors%20should%20only%20prescribe%20generic%20medicines%20except%20in%20certain%20circumstances%20that%20it%20has%20defined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NMC%20guidelines%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20Registered%20Medical%20Practitioner%20should%20prescribe%20drugs%20using%20generic%20names%20written%20legibly%20and%20prescribe%20drugs%20rationally%2C%20avoiding%20unnecessary%20medications%20and%20irrational%20fixed-dose%20combination%20tablets.%E2%80%9D%20The%20NMC%20says%20doctors%20should%20prescribe%20%E2%80%9Cgeneric%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cnon-proprietary%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cpharmacological%E2%80%9D%20names%20only%20and%20they%20should%20%E2%80%98avoid%E2%80%99%20prescribing%20%E2%80%9Cbranded%20generic%20drugs%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20following%20the%20directive%20would%20first%20lead%20to%20an%20advisory%20being%20issued%20to%20a%20doctor%20and%2For%20suspension%20of%20licence%20for%20a%20maximum%20of%20one%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20pure%20generic%20drug%20is%20one%20which%20is%20a%20copy%20of%20an%20innovator%20drug%20%E2%80%93%20it%20has%20no%20company%2Fbrand%20name%20mentioned%20and%20has%20only%20the%20pharmaceutical%20ingredients%20on%20the%20label.%20Branded%20generic%20drugs%20are%20the%20ones%20which%20are%20also%20copies%20of%20the%20innovator%20drug%20but%20have%20a%20brand%20name%20and%20are%20produced%20when%20the%20former%20has%20come%20off%20patent.%20They%20are%20usually%20cheaper%20than%20the%20original%20ones%20and%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20manufactured%20without%20compromising%20safety%20and%20efficacy%20as%20comparable%20to%20the%20original%20drug.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20number%20of%20medical%20doctors%2C%20on%20various%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20have%20shown%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20reluctance%20towards%20the%20NMC%20prescription%20guidelines%2C%20saying%20that%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20enough%20regulation%20for%20ensuring%20quality%20in%20drugs%2C%20especially%20in%20many%20branded%20generic%20medicines%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20%E2%80%98trust%E2%80%99%20certain%20brands%20owing%20to%20feedback%20from%20their%20own%20patients.%20They%20cited%20empirical%20examples%20to%20support%20this.%20And%20the%20regulation%20will%20take%20away%20their%20right%20to%20choose%20the%20prescription%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20another%20section%20of%20voices%20says%20that%20while%20there%20are%20scientific%20studies%20to%20say%20that%20an%20innovator%20brand%20was%20more%20effective%20than%20the%20generics%2C%20not%20every%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20feedback%20is%20based%20on%20such%20studies%20because%20their%20number%20is%20far%20and%20few.%20They%20bring%20into%20the%20fore%20the%20importance%20of%20%E2%80%98access%20to%20medicines%E2%80%99%20as%20generics%20or%20branded%20generics%20are%20cheaper%20than%20the%20original%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20the%20IMA%20has%20said%20that%20the%20new%20notification%20only%20puts%20the%20ball%20in%20the%20court%20of%20the%20chemist%20as%20s%2Fhe%20would%20decide%20which%20drug%20for%20the%20formulation%20prescribed%20by%20the%20doctor%20has%20to%20be%20dispensed%20to%20the%20patient%20%E2%80%94%20rather%20than%20the%20doctor%20taking%20this%20call%20%E2%80%93%20and%20this%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20ensure%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20the%20patient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Grewal%20called%20the%20NMC%20move%20on%20this%20front%20%E2%80%98dishonest%E2%80%99%20if%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20was%20aimed%20at%20reigning%20in%20exorbitant%20trade%20margins%20against%20the%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20a%20report%20which%20was%20submitted%20by%20a%20government-constituted%20committee%20in%20March%202016%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20trade%20margin%20rationalisation%20of%20drugs%2C%20Grewal%20said%20the%20report%20clearly%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20trade%20margins%20could%20be%20capped%20and%20through%20which%20process.%20%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20using%20measures%20such%20as%20those%20suggested%20by%20the%20committee%20and%20without%20bringing%20in%20necessary%20drug%20regulatory%20overhaul%2C%20this%20step%20would%20not%20be%20the%20best%20thing%20for%20patients%20to%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NMC%20rules%20can%20be%20done%20away%20with%20drugs%20which%20are%20biosimilars%2C%20drugs%20with%20narrow%20therapeutic%20index%20(NTI)%20and%20%E2%80%9Cand%20similar%20other%20exceptional%20cases%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20the%20guidelines.%20Biosimilars%20are%20those%20products%20which%20are%20similar%20to%20other%20biologics%20%E2%80%93%20medicines%20made%20of%20living%20entities%20%E2%80%93%20unlike%20other%20medicines%20which%20are%20chemically%20similar%20synthesised%20and%20their%20generic%20or%20copied%20versions%20can%20be%20relatively%20easily%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENTI%20drugs%20are%20the%20ones%20in%20which%20a%20very%20small%20difference%20in%20dosage%20can%20lead%20to%20the%20drug%20being%20rendered%20ineffective%20(if%20present%20in%20small%20amounts%20as%20compared%20to%20what%20is%20said%20in%20the%20label)%20or%20becoming%20toxic%20(if%20present%20in%20a%20greater%20amount).%20In%20other%20words%2C%20if%20doctors%20are%20prescribing%20biosimilars%20or%20drugs%20with%20NTI%2C%20they%20can%20prescribe%20brand%20names%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20next%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIMA%20president%20Dr%20Agarwal%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehe%20was%20%E2%80%9Csatisfied%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20meeting%20with%20Mandaviya%20because%20the%20delegation%20was%20%E2%80%9Cheard%20patiently%E2%80%9D%20as%20far%20as%20the%20two%20demands%20are%20concerned%2C%20and%20was%20told%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20minister%20would%20get%20back%20after%20discussing%20with%20his%20team%E2%80%9D.%20The%20minister%20didn%E2%80%99t%20specify%20any%20timeline%20for%20the%20purpose%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20NMC%20guidelines%20were%20published%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20gazetted%20notification%20on%20August%202.%20On%20being%20asked%20if%20the%20minister%20had%20agreed%20to%20put%20them%20in%20abeyance%20till%20his%20final%20decision%2C%20the%20IMA%20president%20replied%20in%20negative.%20Asked%20how%20doctors%20would%20need%20to%20go%20ahead%20in%20that%20case%2C%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20specify%20except%20for%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20change%20in%20the%20status%20%5Bof%20existence%20of%20guidelines%5D%20before%20or%20after%20the%20meeting.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20wish%20to%20speculate%20on%20the%20next%20course%20of%20action%20by%20the%20powerful%20doctors%E2%80%99%20organisation%20should%20the%20minister%20refuse%20to%20pay%20heed%20to%20its%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692687701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22123040%2Fsasun-bughdaryan-RlIppR1I3E8-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fdoctors-organisations-find-novel-ways-to-organise-conferences-without-pharma-backing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20has%20demanded%20a%20rollback%20of%20the%20National%20Medical%20Commission%20guidelines%20which%20bar%20such%20conferences%20and%20say%20doctors%20must%20prescribe%20generic%20medicines%2C%20and%20the%20health%20minister%20has%20reportedly%20said%20he%20will%20look%20into%20the%20association's%20demands.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fukushima%20nuclear%20disaster%3A%20Japan%20to%20release%20treated%20water%20in%2048%20hours%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692687536000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3E54%2Fproduction%2F_130865951_98b166e750441efd5e81f6d4abe9229f309fd4b8.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66578158%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UN-approved%20plan%20will%20proceed%20