20were%20wrongly%20implicated%20in%20the%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamiat%20Ulema-i-Hind%2C%20only%20a%20socio-religious%20organisation%20until%20then%2C%20soon%20transformed%20into%20a%20legal%20aid%20centre%20for%20men%20across%20India%20implicated%20in%20terror-related%20cases.%20And%20the%20man%20spearheading%20the%20legal%20campaign%20ever%20since%20was%20Gulzar%20Azmi%2C%20a%20senior%20leader%20at%20the%20Jamiat.%20Azmi%20was%2074%20years%20old%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20fall%20and%20a%20subsequent%20head%20injury%2C%20Azmi%20died%20on%20August%2020%20in%20a%20city%20hospital.%20He%20was%2090.%20But%20just%20moments%20before%20his%20fall%2C%20his%20colleagues%20say%20he%20was%20working%20until%20late%20evening%20in%20the%20Jamiat%20office%20at%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Imambada%20Compound.%20In%20his%20over%20a%20decade%20and%20a%20half%E2%80%99s%20work%20as%20secretary%20of%20the%20Jamiat%E2%80%99s%20legal%20cell%2C%20Azmi%20oversaw%20cases%20of%20over%20500%20persons%2C%20all%20implicated%20in%20terror%20cases%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20primary%20principle%20was%20that%20so%20long%20as%20the%20person%20is%20wrongly%20implicated%2C%20we%20have%20to%20offer%20them%20legal%20assistance%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20his%20colleague%2C%20advocate%20Shahid%20Nadeem.%20So%20when%20families%20of%20those%20incarcerated%20approached%20him%2C%20Nadeem%20says%2C%20Azmi%20took%20great%20interest%20in%20finding%20out%20if%20the%20charges%20levelled%20against%20them%20had%20any%20truth%20in%20them.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20his%20death%2C%20Azmi%2C%20along%20with%20the%20legal%20team%20at%20the%20Jamiat%2C%20was%20handling%20cases%20of%20over%2075%20persons%20who%20have%20been%20awarded%20the%20death%20sentence%2C%20and%20over%20125%20life%20convicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzmi%20was%20not%20a%20lawyer.%20He%20had%20in%20fact%20only%20studied%20till%20class%205.%20But%20because%20of%20his%20legal%20knowledge%2C%20people%20mistook%20him%20for%20a%20lawyer%2C%20Nadeem%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20Azamgarh%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Azmi%20spent%20most%20of%20his%20life%20in%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Bhendi%20Bazar%20area%2C%20a%20predominantly%20Muslim%20locality.%20At%20a%20very%20young%20age%2C%20he%20got%20involved%20in%20the%20socialist%20movement%20and%20became%20a%20part%20of%20many%20socio-religious%20groups.%20He%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20Jamiat%20Ulema%20since%20the%201950s.%20For%20over%2065%20years%2C%20he%20served%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20his%20colleagues%20recall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22111918%2FDSC_5641.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22111918%2FDSC_5641.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22111918%2FDSC_5641-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22111918%2FDSC_5641-1024x684.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669097%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22801%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGulzar%20Azmi%E2%80%99s%20funeral.%20Photo%3A%20Imtiyaz%20Shaikh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWahid%20Shaikh%2C%20who%20was%20falsely%20implicated%20in%20the%20July%2011%2C%202006%20Mumbai%20serial%20train%20blast%20case%20and%20was%20incarcerated%20for%20over%20nine%20years%2C%20says%20Azmi%E2%80%99s%20work%20gave%20hopes%20to%20hundreds%20of%20those%20families%20who%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20fight%20the%20might%20of%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20you%20are%20arrested%2C%20the%20fight%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20just%20the%20trial%20court.%20One%20has%20to%20fight%20it%20all%20the%20way%20up%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20And%20most%20families%20can%E2%80%99t%20imagine%20this%20arduous%20legal%20battle%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shaikh%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaikh%20says%20Azmi%20came%20with%20respectable%20stature%20and%20was%20known%20to%20have%20close%20associations%20with%20political%20leaders%20across%20parties.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20to%20his%20rescue%20when%20his%20two%20nephews%20were%20arrested%20in%20a%20MCOCA%20%5BMaharashtra%20Control%20of%20Organised%20Crime%20Act%5D%C2%A0case%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shaikh%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20Azmi%20spent%20time%20building%20a%20legal%20team%20across%20every%20state%20in%20the%20country.%20This%20team%20of%20lawyers%20has%20been%20handling%20most%20terror-related%20cases%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20right%20from%20the%20trial%20court%20level%20up%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20One%20of%20the%20first%20lawyers%20to%20work%20with%20him%20was%20Shahid%20Azmi%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20in%202010%20allegedly%20by%20gangster%20Chhota%20Rajan%E2%80%99s%20aides.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20his%20death%2C%20Shahid%20was%20representing%20several%20accused%20in%20the%207%2F11%20train%20blasts%20cases%2C%20Malegaon%202006%20bomb%20blasts%20cases%2C%20the%20Aurangabad%20arms%20haul%20case%2C%20the%20Ghatkopar%20blasts%20case%20and%20the%20November%2026%2C%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20attack%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Shahid%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20Azmi%20started%20a%20scholarship%20for%20students%20interested%20in%20pursuing%20law.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20year%2C%20the%20Jamiat%20has%20been%20sponsoring%20studies%20of%2025-30%20law%20students%20from%20the%20Muslim%20and%20Dalit%20communities.%20Azmi%20believed%20that%20besides%20helping%20those%20arrested%2C%20the%20community%20needs%20its%20own%20lawyers%20to%20fight%20against%20the%20injustice%20meted%20out%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nadeem%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20time%20the%20police%20claimed%20to%20have%20cracked%20a%20new%20terror%20module%2C%20Azmi%20would%20tap%20his%20local%20networks%2C%20find%20out%20the%20background%20of%20those%20implicated%20and%20work%20out%20a%20legal%20strategy%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22112131%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-21-at-10.21.28-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22112131%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-21-at-10.21.28-AM.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22112131%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-21-at-10.21.28-AM-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669098%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20Mufti%20Abdul%20Qayyum%20Mansuri%2C%20who%20was%20awarded%20the%20death%20penalty%20in%20the%20Akshardham%20blast%20case%20only%20to%20be%20later%20acquitted%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20needed%20legal%20assistance%2C%20Azmi%20was%20the%20first%20person%20to%20reach%20out.%20%E2%80%9CAzmi%20%3Cem%3Esahab%3C%2Fem%3E%20came%20to%20see%20me%20and%20other%20men%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20in%20Sabarmati%20jail.%20He%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20but%20he%20did.%20He%20assured%20us%20that%20the%20Jamiat%20will%20take%20care%20of%20the%20case.%20And%20he%20did%20till%20the%20very%20end%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mansuri%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMansuri%20was%20in%20Mumbai%20to%20attend%20Azmi%E2%80%99s%20funeral.%20Thousands%20turned%20up%20to%20pay%20homage%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20were%20persons%20accused%20of%20terror%20crimes%20and%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamiat%20Ulema-i-Hind%20is%20a%20donor-driven%20organisation%20and%20every%20year%20during%20Eid%2C%20many%20people%20from%20the%20community%20offer%20%3Cem%3Ezakat%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20customary%202.5%25%20of%20the%20total%20income%20offered%20to%20the%20poor%20and%20needy)%20to%20the%20organisation.%20The%20organisation%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20have%20a%20smooth%20run.%20In%202014%2C%20BJP%20MLA%20Ashish%20Shelar%20kicked%20up%20a%20storm%20by%20urging%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20to%20ban%20the%20Jamiat%20Ulema-i-Hind.%20Shelar%20accused%20Azmi%20of%20having%20links%20with%20fugitive%20gangster%20Chhota%20Shakeel.%20The%20statement%20led%20to%20furore%20and%20eventually%20Shelar%20was%20forced%20to%20withdraw%20his%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692683541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22111800%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-21-at-3.38.22-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhow-gulzar-azmi-helped-wrongly-implicated-terror-accused-fight-for-justice-across-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Under%20Azmi's%20watch%2C%20the%20Jamiat%20Ulema-I-Hind%20transformed%20from%20a%20socio-religious%20to%20a%20legal%20aid%20organisation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhow-gulzar-azmi-helped-wrongly-implicated-terror-accused-fight-for-justice-across-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-PM%20Thaksin%20jailed%20on%20return%20to%20Thailand%20after%2015%20years%20in%20exile%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692683207000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102931106%2Cimgsize-1291063.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fex-pm-thaksin-jailed-on-return-to-thailand-after-15-years-in-exile%2Farticleshow%2F102931143.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left