adu%20have%20already%20rejected%20the%20NEP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHigher%20education%20minister%20M.C.%20Sudhakar%20said%20no%20names%20were%20proposed%20or%20discussed%20in%20the%20meeting%20for%20the%20expert%20committee.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20consider%20all%20stakeholders%20while%20framing%20the%20policy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20According%20to%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20is%20likely%20to%20refer%20to%20an%20October%202016%20report%20on%20Karnataka%20State%20Education%20Policy%20prepared%20by%20the%20former%20Karnataka%20Knowledge%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20had%20already%20confirmed%20that%20the%20NEP%20would%20be%20withdrawn%20next%20year%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20election%20manifesto%20promise%20over%20the%20controversial%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20policy%20would%20be%20for%20primary%20and%20higher%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20was%20taken%20after%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20of%20Karnataka%20government%20officials%2C%20academics%20and%20vice-chancellors%20of%20the%20universities%2C%20Shivakumar%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20decided%20to%20scrap%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%2C%20which%20has%20been%20adopted%20by%20the%20BJP%20government.%20Next%20year%2C%20we%20are%20coming%20out%20with%20the%20new%20Karnataka%20Education%20Policy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shivakumar%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20said%20after%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fwe-have-decided-to-scrap-national-education-policy-adopted-by-bjp-government-d-k-shivakumar%2Fcid%2F1960606%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Ca%20special%20committee%20would%20be%20launched%20next%20week%20to%20work%20out%20the%20details%20of%20the%20proposed%20state%20policy%E2%80%9D%20in%20keeping%20with%20future%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202021%2C%20under%20a%20BJP-led%20government%2C%20Karnataka%20was%20the%20first%20state%20to%20adopt%20the%20NEP%20in%20higher%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEP%20has%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20pushback%20from%20southern%20states%2C%20seeing%20themselves%20as%20centres%20of%20education%20and%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20in%20April%2C%20the%20curriculum%20steering%20committee%20meeting%20of%20the%20Kerala%20State%20Council%20of%20Educational%20Research%20and%20Training%20(SCERT)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-govt-to-include-ncert-omitted-portions-in-state-school-syllabus-101682500160057.html%5C%22%3Ehad%20issued%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20announcing%20that%20it%20had%20decided%20to%20include%20the%20portions%20omitted%20by%20the%20National%20Council%20of%20Educational%20Research%20and%20Training%20(NCERT)%20in%20the%20state%20school%20syllabus.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-govt-to-include-ncert-omitted-portions-in-state-school-syllabus-101682500160057.html%5C%22%3EEducation%20minister%20V.%20Sivankutty%20has%20also%20said%20that%20the%20state%20will%20include%20omitted%20portions%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Kerala%20school%20syllabus.%20NCERT%20has%20excluded%20Mughal%20history%2C%20Gujarat%20riots%20and%20Darwin%E2%80%99s%20theory%20of%20evolution%20from%20school%20textbooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20had%20formed%20a%2013%20-member%20committee%20in%20June%202022%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Farticleshow%2F100380528.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%26utm_source%3Dcontentofinterest%26utm_medium%3Dtext%26utm_campaign%3Dcppst%5C%22%3Eto%20frame%20a%20distinct%20state%20education%20policy.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Headed%20by%20retired%20chief%20justice%20D.%20Murugesan%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20to%20file%20its%20report%20by%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692678951000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F