tance%20could%20be%20extended%20to%20MPs%20through%20the%20identified%20protocol%20officer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fzeenews.india.com%2Faviation%2Findigo-boss-rahul-bhatia-summoned-for-not-extending-privilege-facilities-to-ministers-2651805.html%5C%22%3EZee%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20issues%20of%20protocol-related%20%E2%80%9Cnegligence%E2%80%9D%20had%20been%20raised%20in%202021%20as%20well%2C%20and%20the%20civil%20aviation%20ministry%20had%20then%20asked%20all%20airlines%20and%20airports%20to%20follow%20the%20set%20out%20protocol%20that%20provides%20special%20treatment%20to%20MPs%20when%20they%20travel.%20Former%20civil%20aviation%20minister%20Ashok%20Gajapathi%20Raju%20had%20said%20in%202015%20that%20this%20treatment%20is%20provided%20as%20a%20courtesy%20and%20not%20a%20privilege.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692677741000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findigo-md-rahul-bhatia-summoned-by-lok-sabha-panel-over-protocol-violations-involving-mps%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22No%20details%20have%20been%20made%20public%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20these%20%26quot%3Bviolations%26quot%3B%2C%20nor%20is%20it%20clear%20what%20the%20legal%20basis%20is%20for%20a%20parliamentary%20committee%20to%20direct%20private%20airlines%20to%20treat%20some%20passengers%2C%20i.e.%20MPs%2C%20better%20than%20others.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indigo%20MD%20Rahul%20Bhatia%20Summoned%20By%20Lok%20Sabha%20Panel%20Over%20'Protocol%20Violations'%20Involving%20MPs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F22093151%2FAirbus_A320-232_IndiGo_Airlines_JP7701002.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Lok%20Sab