8150906%2FSupreme-Court.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Gujarat%20high%20court%20for%20its%20handling%20of%20a%2025-year-old%20rape%20survivor%E2%80%99s%20plea%20for%20an%20abortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%20(August%2021)%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20B.V.%20Nagarathna%20and%C2%A0Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20allowed%20the%20woman%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20pregnancy%20termination%2C%20as%20she%20was%20deemed%20medically%20fit%20for%20the%20procedure.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20hearing%20the%20woman%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20on%20the%20matter%20after%20a%20single-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20high%20court%20had%20rejected%20her%20petition%20on%20August%2017%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fwhat-happening-gujarat-high-court-supreme-court-objects-counterblast-order%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20informed%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20high%20court%20too%20had%20heard%20the%20matter%20on%20Saturday%2C%20and%20passed%20an%20order%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order%20for%20a%20medical%20examination%20the%20same%20day.%20The%20high%20court%20order%20had%20rejected%20the%20abortion%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20supporting%20this%3F%20We%20do%20not%20appreciate%20the%20high%20court%20passing%20an%20order%20as%20a%20counterblast%20to%20our%20order.%20Thank%20you%20for%20bringing%20it%20to%20our%20notice%2C%20but%20are%20you%20supporting%3F%20What%20is%20happening%20in%20Gujarat%20high%20court%3F%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20asked%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20disposed%20of%20matter%2C%20it%C2%A0(high%20court)%20passed%20again%3F%20How%3F%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Bhuyan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20court%20in%20India%20can%20pass%20an%20order%20like%20this%20on%20a%20Saturday%20against%20a%20superior%20court%20order.%20Without%20giving%20notice%20to%20the%20other%20side%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20need%20for%20the%20high%20court%20to%20justify%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Gujarat%20government%2C%20claimed%20that%20there%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cclerical%20error%E2%80%9D%20that%20led%20to%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20second%20order%20on%20the%20matter.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20lords%20may%20leave%20it%20at%20that.%20There%20was%20a%20misunderstanding%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20unconvinced%20by%20this%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fwhat-is-happening-in-gujarat-high-court-we-dont-appreciate-hcs-counterblast-to-our-order-supreme-court-in-abortion-case-235689%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20been%20unhappy%20with%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20overall%20approach%20in%20the%20case%2C%20calling%20it%20%E2%80%9Clackadaisical%E2%80%9D.%20The%20court%20had%20first%20adjourned%20the%20matter%20by%2012%20days%20despite%20its%20urgency%2C%20and%20then%20advanced%20the%20hearing%20to%20August%2017%20when%20it%20summarily%20dismissed%20the%20petition.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20asked%20the%20high%20court%20registry%20to%20answer%20for%20this%2C%20saying%20the%20woman%20had%20lost%20%E2%80%9Cvaluable%20time%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692676253000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-comes-down-heavily-on-gujarat-hc-for-its-handling-of-rape-survivors-abortion-petition%22%2C%22summary%2