0could%20be%20lost%20to%20the%20tech.%3Cp%3EGuillaume%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EArtificial%20intelligence%20is%20unlikely%20to%20destroy%20jobs%2C%20per%20the%20International%20Labour%20Organization.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20in%20high-income%20countries%2C%2021%20million%20jobs%20held%20by%20women%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20automated.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E3%25%20of%20jobs%20in%20high-income%20countries%20held%20by%20men%20face%20the%20potential%20of%20being%20automated.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-jobs-at-risk-replacement-artificial-intelligence-ai-labor-trends-2023-02%5C%22%3Egrowing%20fears%20across%20sectors%20of%20being%20replaced%20by%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ilo.org%2Fglobal%2Fabout-the-ilo%2Fnewsroom%2Fnews%2FWCMS_890740%2Flang--en%2Findex.htm%5C%22%3Enew%20study%20by%20the%20International%20Labour%20Organization%2C%20or%20ILO%2C%20published%20on%20Monday%3C%2Fa%3E%20finds%20admin%20workers%20and%20women%20face%20a%20greater%20risk%20of%20their%20jobs%20being%20replaced%20by%20the%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20effects%20of%20automation%20are%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20gendered%2C%20with%20more%20than%20double%20the%20share%20of%20women%20potentially%20affected%20by%20automation%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20high-income%20countries%2C%207.8%25%20of%20jobs%20held%20by%20women%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20automated%20%E2%80%94%20which%20the%20ILO%20estimates%20to%20be%20around%2021%20million%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%202.9%25%20of%20jobs%20in%20high-income%20countries%20held%20by%20men%20%E2%80%94%20or%20around%209%20million%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20face%20the%20potential%20of%20being%20automated%2C%20as%20shown%20in%20the%20graf%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221718%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22International%20Labour%20Organization%20graph%20on%20jobs%20with%20automation%20potential%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e429e2b698ac0019debcec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221158%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInternational%20Labour%20Organization%20graph%20on%20jobs%20with%20automation%20potential%3Cp%3EInternational%20Labour%20Organization%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EClerical%20support%20workers%20also%20face%20the%20greatest%20risk%20of%20being%20affected%20by%20AI.%20About%20a%20quarter%20of%20clerical%20workers'%20tasks%20face%20a%20high%20exposure%20to%20generative%20AI%2C%20and%2058%25%20of%20their%20tasks%20face%20a%20medium%20exposure%20to%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20listed%20jobs%20such%20as%20typists%2C%20travel%20consultants%2C%20scribes%2C%20contact%20center%20information%20clerks%2C%20bank%20tellers%2C%20and%20survey%20and%20market%20research%20interviewers%20that%20could%20eventually%20be%20automated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20however%2C%20most%20workers'%20tasks%C2%A0are%20not%20majorly%20at%20risk%20from%20AI%2C%20the%20study%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20study%20found%20that%20only%204%25%20of%20service%20and%20sales%20workers'%20tasks%20face%20high%20exposure%20to%20generative%20AI%2C%20and%2018%25%20of%20their%20tasks%20face%20medium%20exposure.%20%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20the%20greatest%20impact%20of%20this%20technology%20is%20likely%20to%20not%20be%20job%20destruction%20but%20rather%20the%20potential%20changes%20to%20the%20quality%20of%20jobs%2C%20notably%20work%20intensity%20and%20autonomy%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20used%20GPT-4%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgpt4-openai-chatgpt-everything-you-need-to-know-4-2023-3%5C%22%3Ethe%20large%20language%20model%20behind%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20predict%20how%20jobs%20might%20be%20automated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20also%20noted%20that%20AI's%20%26quot%3Bsocioeconomic%20impacts%20will%20largely%20depend%20on%20how%20its%20diffusion%20is%20managed%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20costs%20to%20affected%20workers%20could%20be%20%26quot%3Bbrutal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20study%20adds%20to%20past%20research%20on%20how%20AI%20could%20disrupt%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-automation-destroy-white-collar-jobs-careers-2023-7%5C%22%3EJuly%20study%20by%20McKinsey%20also%20found%20that%20generative%20AI%20could%20benefit%20white%20collar%20in%20the%20long%20run%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead%20of%20replacing%20them%2C%20while%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-chatpgt-300-million-full-time-jobs-goldman-sachs-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Goldman%20Sachs%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-chatpgt-300-million-full-time-jobs-goldman-sachs-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-chatpgt-300-million-full-time-jobs-goldman-sachs-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20in%20March%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20administrative%20staff%20were%20at%20particular%20risk%20from%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-unlikely-destroy-jobs-admin-workers-greatest-risk-chatgpt-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692674676000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63dd2362e33c4000193ad336%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-unlikely-destroy-jobs-admin-workers-greatest-risk-chatgpt-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20study%20by%20the%20ILO%20published%20on%20Monday%20finds%20adm