-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20it%20takes%20to%20run%20the%20estate%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERubbishing%20the%20usual%20assumption%20that%20coffee%20planters%20lead%20luxurious%20lives%2C%20Shreedev%20says%20that%20it%20is%20not%20that%20simple%20or%20rosy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20our%20quality%20of%20life%20is%20very%20good%20but%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20that%20goes%20into%20it.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F90205%2F10-sustainable-homestays-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFarming%20on%20plantations%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20hard.%20Managing%20250%20acres%20of%20land%20is%20tough.%20And%20that%20is%20the%20side%20that%20few%20see%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20every%20night%20after%20a%20tedious%20and%20laborious%20day%20at%20the%20plantations%2C%20Shreedev%20returns%20home%20with%20freshly-harvested%20coffee%20beans%20%E2%80%94%20that%20the%20guests%20wait%20eagerly%20for%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20satisfaction.%20The%20plantations%20are%20where%20he%20belongs%2C%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurrounded%20by%20the%20plantations%2C%20Woodway%2C%20with%20its%20six%20fully-furnished%20rooms%20replete%20with%20modern%20amenities%20that%20complement%20the%20old-world%20charm%2C%20also%20houses%20a%20kitchen%20garden.%20The%20couple%20started%20working%20on%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297379%2Fcouple-set-up-eco-friendly-homestay-in-nilgiris-jungle-hut-harvests-solar-power%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassion%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202000%2C%20fixing%20the%20roof%2C%20electrical%20lines%20and%20painting%2C%20while%20preserving%20the%20original%20look%20and%20feel%20of%20the%20home.%20Shreedev%20gives%20the%20credit%20of%20overseeing%20the%20restoration%20to%20Susmitha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigur