C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20reject%20his%20queer%20identity%2C%20but%20did%20say%20one%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CApne%20mein%20chalta%20hai%2C%20bahar%20jaake%20mat%20karna%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20and%20it%20was%20Pride%20Month%20in%20Mumbai.%20Navin%20and%20his%20partner%20were%20photographed%20kissing%20each%20other%20on%20the%20front%20page%20of%20%3Cem%3EBombay%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20a%20cousin%20he%20dislikes%2C%20a%20screenshot%20of%20that%20photo%20was%20shared%20on%20the%20family%20WhatsApp%20group.%20Furious%20at%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20extended%20family%20finding%20out%20that%20her%20son%20is%20gay%2C%20Navin%E2%80%99s%20mother%20once%20again%20repeated%20that%20maxim%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20kicked%20him%20out%20of%20the%20house.%20Despite%20the%20initial%20pain%2C%20there%20was%20also%20a%20sense%20of%20relief%20for%20Navin.%20He%20and%20his%20partner%20ended%20up%20finding%20an%20apartment%20and%20started%20living%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLook%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20called%20a%20pioneer%20of%20queer%20comedy%20or%20anything%20like%20that.%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20queer%20community.%20I%E2%80%99m%20saying%20this%20is%20my%20story%20and%20the%20question%20is%20whether%20we%20can%20relate%20on%20different%20issues%20and%20share%20in%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20happiness%20or%20misery.%20The%20bit%20on%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Apne%20mein%20chalta%20hai%E2%80%A6%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20not%20just%20a%20queer%20thing%2C%20but%20represents%20a%20much%20bigger%20picture%20of%20how%20South%20Asian%20kids%20live.%20If%20people%20can%20connect%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20coming%20out%20to%20your%20parents%20at%20any%20level%20is%20difficult%2C%20then%20we%E2%80%99ve%20won%20on%20that%20front%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E